{"tid":2015770,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"九東立法會有本土素人都唔投？你地傻左呀","createTime":"2020-05-14T02:35:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T06:23:11.000Z","uid":84308,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"56f91199bd75a6841187b4b487f1230cdc810cf7","tid":2015770,"uid":84308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T02:35:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌仲喺度問有無本土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同我睇哂佢<br />\n<br />\n李嘉達立場投稿我篇篇都有睇<br />\n<br />\n港獨不可能？我似乎開心得太早－2047前的時代責任<br />\n不談港獨，也談香港自主<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/不談港獨-也談香港自主/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E4%B8%8D%E8%AB%87%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8-%E4%B9%9F%E8%AB%87%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%AA%E4%B8%BB%2F&d=xUEPa7L8eIFrsai6sDUjHJB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=e54c2040\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E4%B8%8D%E8%AB%87%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8-%E4%B9%9F%E8%AB%87%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%AA%E4%B8%BB%2F&h=2f05faa2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/不談港獨-也談香港自主/</a><br />\n<br />\n只投本土okay?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n將香港點樣自主處理資源問題 詳細咁列晒解決方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全力撐真.素人<br />\n<br />\n/此文旨在拋磚引玉，望引起讀者一同想像在光復香港以後，香港應如何發展，畢竟文章開初提到的藍絲網民所提出的糧食及食水問題，是實際不過、有待解決的難題；而香港的經濟轉型，更是我們這代香港人，除了政治改革之外，另一個時代責任。最後回應那位藍絲網民，我們這代香港人沒有太多「建立家庭」的意欲，是因為我們不希望將下一代帶到這個「不自主」的香港。/"},{"pid":"3223944c8c07966170d78273d1a404e692639827","tid":2015770,"uid":78184,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T02:39:20.000Z","msg":"初選過到先講"},{"pid":"e21a570426d58ad9441a7bda3de84f253a34144b","tid":2015770,"uid":84308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T02:40:12.000Z","msg":"召集九東人"},{"pid":"0d83426368c8c53f718400f03c3d6cc300dbe350","tid":2015770,"uid":84308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14